STATE of North Carolina
v.
Michael Alonzo BANNERMAN. No. 142P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 17, 2005. Michael Alonzo Bannerman, Pro Se. William D. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, Mitchell D. Norton, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 10th day of March 2005 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Washington County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 17th day of March 2005."
